ri Bottas]]'''\n|'''[[Mercedes-Benz in Formula One|Mercedes]]'''\n|44\n| +16.456\n|3\n|align=\"center\"|'''10'''\n|-\n!6\n|align=\"center\"|27\n|{{flagicon|GER}} '''[[Nico H\u00fclkenberg]]'''\n|'''[[Renault in Formula One|Renault]]'''\n|44\n| +28.087\n|7\n|align=\"center\"| '''8'''\n|-\n!7\n|align=\"center\"|8\n|{{flagicon|FRA}} '''[[Romain Grosjean]]'''\n|'''[[Haas F1 Team|Haas]]'''-'''[[Scuderia Ferrari|Ferrari]]'''\n|44\n| +31.553\n|11\n|align=\"center\"| '''6'''\n|-\n!8\n|align=\"center\"|19\n|{{flagicon|BRA}} '''[[Felipe Massa]]'''\n|'''[[Williams Grand Prix Engineering|Williams]]'''-'''[[Mercedes AMG High Performance Powertrains|Mercedes]]'''\n|44\n| +36.649\n|16\n|align=\"center\"| '''4'''\n|-\n!9\n|align=\"center\"|31\n|{{flagicon|FRA}} '''[[Esteban Ocon]]'''\n|{{nowrap|'''[[Force India]]-[[Mercedes AMG High Performance Powertrains|Mercedes]]'''}}\n|44\n| +38.154\n|9\n|align=\"center\"| '''2'''\n|-\n!10\n|align=\"center\"|55\n|{{flagicon|ESP}} '''[[Carlos Sainz Jr.]]'''\n|'''[[Scuderia Toro Rosso|Toro Rosso]]'''\n|44\n| +39.447\n|13\n|align=\"center\"|'''1'''\n|-\n!11\n|align=\"center\"|18\n|{{flagicon|CAN}} [[Lance Stroll]]\n|[[Williams Grand Prix Engineering|Williams]]-[[Mercedes AMG High Performance Powertrains|Mercedes]]  \n|44\n| +48.999\n|15\n|align=\"center\"|\n|-\n!12\n|align=\"center\"|26\n|{{flagicon|RUS}} [[Daniil Kvyat]]\n|[[Scuderia Toro Rosso|Toro Rosso]]\n|44\n| +49.940\n|19\n|align=\"center\"|\n|-\n!13\n|align=\"center\"|30\n|{{flagicon|GBR}} [[Jolyon Palmer]]\n|[[Renault in Formula One|Renault]]\n|44\n| +53.239\n|14\n|align=\"center\"|\n|-\n!14\n|align=\"center\"|2\n|{{nowrap|{{flagicon|BEL}} [[Stoffel Vandoorne]]}}\n|[[McLaren]]-[[Honda in Formula One|Honda]]\n|44\n| +57.078\n|20\n| \n|-\n!15\n|align=\"center\"|20\n|{{flagicon|DEN}} [[Kevin Magnussen]]\n|[[Haas F1 Team|Haas]]-[[Scuderia Ferrari|Ferrari]]\n|44\n| +1:07.262\n|12\n|align=\"center\"|\n|-\n!16\n|align=\"center\"|9\n|{{flagicon|SWE}} [[Marcus Ericsson]]\n|[[Sauber]]-[[Scuderia F